column5: http://www.weatheroffice.gc.ca/warnings/warnings_e.html Be sure to take care and cover should Momma Nature pick your spot on the planet to whack the crap out of.... HH

This is the time when mother nature can spin her fury. We up here know to well what can come, with these warm humid temps. Been watching the skys all day,and it is starting to cool down. Not a good mix.
Anyone from or near Lucus London? They got one yesturday.
Nice thunderstorm in Toronto now, looks like some more later tonight and tomorrow. Nothing severe right now just nice lightening and rumbles of thunder for a summer night feel.
